Template to create vm
New-AzVm
       -ResourceGroupName <resource group name>
       -Name <machine name>
       -Credential <credentials object>
       -Location <location>
       -Image <image name>
       -OpenPorts <port>
       -PublicIpAddressName <publicaddressname>